---
title: Greek-Inspired Lamb Chops with Lemon-Garlic Potatoes and Pepper Salad
description: Classic Mediterranean flavours are on the menu tonight with lemon-pepper roasted potatoes, spiced lamb chops and a fresh Greek-style salad. Wrap bites of everything into garlicky flatbreads and dunk it into a side of tzatziki.
